124
00:09:03,342 --> 00:09:11,350
[car and street noise]

125
00:09:13,319 --> 00:09:14,820
Do you see him?

126
00:09:14,854 --> 00:09:22,862
I see him.

127
00:09:24,163 --> 00:09:25,097
