133
00:09:36,342 --> 00:09:44,350
[car noise]

134
00:09:46,385 --> 00:09:54,393
[car noise]

135
00:09:54,961 --> 00:10:01,067
[puts car into park]

136
00:10:01,100 --> 00:10:09,108
[silence]

137
00:10:11,143 --> 00:10:19,151
[silence]

138
00:10:22,154 --> 00:10:24,423
