140
00:10:27,460 --> 00:10:32,732
[crickets chirping]

141
00:10:32,765 --> 00:10:34,467
Get your camera.

142
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:39,905
Okay.

143
00:10:39,939 --> 00:10:41,107
[door opens]

144
00:10:41,140 --> 00:10:42,875
[crickets chirping]

145
00:10:42,908 --> 00:10:44,443
Wait a minute.

146
00:10:44,477 --> 00:10:46,345
