[door creaks open]

152
00:11:07,133 --> 00:11:08,267
[door closes]

153
00:11:08,300 --> 00:11:09,301
Where's he at?

154
00:11:09,335 --> 00:11:12,271
He's upstairs.

155
00:11:12,304 --> 00:11:20,312
[foot steps through the house]

156
