159
00:11:39,031 --> 00:11:40,099
It's him.

160
00:11:40,132 --> 00:11:41,934
Yeah, it's him.

161
00:11:41,967 --> 00:11:44,370
Where's his wife?

162
00:11:44,403 --> 00:11:46,906
She died a few years back.

163
00:11:46,939 --> 00:11:49,975
[heavy breathing]

164
00:11:50,009 --> 00:11:52,978
He's here all by himself now.

165
00:11:53,012 --> 00:12:01,020
[heavy breathing]

166
00:12:02,822 --> 00:12:06,125
Now, I'm gonna
take the tape off.

167
00:12:06,158 --> 00:12:08,861
But if you yell for help or
if you do anything stupid,

168
00:12:08,894 --> 00:12:10,196
I'll end it.

169
00:12:10,229 --> 00:12:13,833
You understand?

170
00:12:13,866 --> 00:12:15,301
[groans]

171
00:12:15,334 --> 00:12:17,870
Take whatever you
want and leave.

172
00:12:17,903 --> 00:12:22,408
This is very manageable for you
two as long as this doesn't go

173
00:12:22,441 --> 00:12:26,212
any further than a robbery.

174
00:12:26,245 --> 00:12:28,848
What makes you think
we're here to rob you?

175
00:12:28,881 --> 00:12:32,284
What is it that you want?

176
00:12:32,318 --> 00:12:34,320
You tell me.

177
00:12:34,353 --> 00:12:38,157
I don't know.

178
00:12:38,190 --> 00:12:39,258
You don't know?

179
00:12:39,291 --> 00:12:40,392
No.

180
00:12:40,426 --> 00:12:43,395
[heavy breathing]

181
00:12:43,429 --> 00:12:45,064
Well you're a judge.

182
00:12:45,097 --> 00:12:46,165
Yes.

183
00:12:46,198 --> 00:12:48,000
Yes I am.

184
00:12:48,033 --> 00:12:51,971
Then it's your job... your
"gift"... to take the evidence

185
00:12:52,004 --> 00:12:55,107
