241
00:16:24,717 --> 00:16:26,218
You wanna stop?

242
00:16:26,251 --> 00:16:28,754
[radio chatter]

243
00:16:28,787 --> 00:16:31,757
No.

244
00:16:31,790 --> 00:16:32,458
[radio chatter]

245
00:16:32,491 --> 00:16:35,160
I remember you loved that place.

246
00:16:35,194 --> 00:16:38,397
Mom would take me there when
you and Andrea were at school.

247
00:16:38,430 --> 00:16:40,399
She'd let me play the video
games and then we'd get

248
00:16:40,432 --> 00:16:44,336
