255
00:17:15,534 --> 00:17:23,542
[sounds of nature]

256
00:17:24,243 --> 00:17:27,713
John?

257
00:17:27,746 --> 00:17:31,550
I remember dad brought
the three of us here.

258
00:17:31,583 --> 00:17:35,521
You were at short,
Andrea was at second,

259
00:17:35,554 --> 00:17:39,792
I was right here on
pitcher's mound.

260
00:17:39,825 --> 00:17:42,327
